@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title Aave Risk-Management Evolution

start
:2020 - On-chain governance;
note right
  Risk managers recommend,
  stakeholders vote, timelock.
  Resilient but slow, not scalable.
end note

:2023 - Manual risk stewards;
note right
  Delegate bounded parameters
  to a trusted operator.
  Efficient but trust-based.
end note

:2024 - First-gen risk oracles;
note right
  Automated operator, encoded
  methodology, bounded updates.
  But an opaque black box.
end note

:Protocol-owned risk oracle (CRE);
note right
  Transparent, node-validated,
  workflow owned by the protocol.
end note

stop
@enduml
